ActionBarManager
Solves the problem of handling multiple actionbars at once.
With Audience.sendActionBar(Component), one actionbar would remove another actionbar.
With the ActionBarManager, it is possible to display multiple actionbars at once.

ManagedEntity<ENTITY_TYPE>
This class provides a manager for entities.
It allows to schedule tasks for entities and works as managed listener.
The goal of this class is to allow scheduling tasks and listen to events while the entity is alive, and then auto-cleanup tasks and listeners when the entity is dead.
DO NOT REGISTER THIS ENTITY DIRECTLY TO THE BUKKIT EVENT LISTENER!!!

SubcommandCommand
A command that can has multiple commands as subcommands.
You can add subcommands with
ungültiges @link 
{@link this#addSubcommand(String, SubcommandEntry)
}.
You can remove subcommands with
ungültiges @link 
{@link this#removeSubcommand(String)
}.
You can set a global permission for the command in the constructor
You can set a DynamicSubcommandProvider that can provide subcommands dynamically in the constructor.
You can override
ungültiges @link 
{@link this#onExecutionWithoutSubcommand(CommandSender, Command, String)
} to run code when the command is executed without subcommands.
